      "text": "（結局、すずは怜が働くスーパーで呼び込みや）\n（試食コーナーなどを担当することになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(In the end‚ Suzu was hired at the supermarket where Rei works)\n(to hand out samples and attract customers.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.166666666666671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（事実上、スーパーのバイトみたいなものだが）\n（事務所を通した“アイドルの営業”として契約を結んだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(While it’s technically a part-time job at a supermarket‚)\n(we made a contract stating it’s “idol sales” through our agency.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 14.700000000000005
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 14.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 14.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "そこの方々！　この成宮すずが呼び込みをする\nスーパータケミヤによく来ました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ladies and gentlemen! Welcome to the supermarket\nwhere I‚ Suzu Narumiya‚ am working!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 22.542017904917362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "このお店、外見はこんなにみすぼらしいですけど\n成宮家の令嬢であるこの私が盛り上げますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This store’s outward appearance may be shabby‚\nbut I‚ the heiress to the Narumiya clan‚ shall jazz it up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.142017904917395,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 20257.982095082596,
          "startTime": 42.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 30.046469653669284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "もう、見ていられないわよ！\n私がお手本を見せるから、こっちに来なさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t stand to watch anymore!\nI’ll show you how it’s done. Get over here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.14646965366924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 36.679802987002574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！？　ちょっと、なんですの！\n私のマイク……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?! Wait‚ what is the meaning of this?\nThat’s my mic!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.11313632033591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 40.82164727551068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "もうっ！\n本番はこれからですのにっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well!\nI was just getting to the good part!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.83443719250289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 43.98831394217737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "今はタイムセールで、ブリがお買い得だから……\n……すう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since yellowtail is on sale for a limited time right now…\nAhh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.92164727551071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 50.25498060884405
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 50.76573858873664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "オトクッ！　オトクッ！\nイマダケオトクッ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Going cheap! Going cheap!\nCatch it while it’s cheap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.09907192206993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 53.82438231581205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ブリッ！　ブリッ！　ブリッ！\nニワリビキィッ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yellowtail! Yellowtail! Yellowtail!\nTwenty percent off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.29104898247874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 56.735529878474786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（アルバイトのレベルを超えた見事な呼び込みだ）\n（怜のプロ根性がここでも発揮されるとは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Her excellent salesmanship is beyond the level of a part-time worker!)\n(I didn’t expect to see Rei’s professionalism manifest itself here of all places.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.93552987847482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　すずも続けて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There! Suzu‚ you do the rest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.49402321716568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 65.75107540031695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "……へ？\nそれ、私もやるんですの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nAm I supposed to do that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.45107540031691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 69.4399643262932
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前でしょ！　さあ！\nオトクッ！　オトクッ！　イマダケオトクッ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course you are! Come on!\nGoing cheap! Going cheap! Catch it while it’s cheap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.03996432629316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 75.2732976596265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "お、おとくっ、おとくっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "G-going cheap. Going cheap…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2732976596265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "声が小さ過ぎる！　もっと大きく！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re too quiet! Louder!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.73765145944644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 78.73765145944647
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 82.17343365358401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "ぶ、ぶりっ！　ぶりっ！　ぶりっ！\nに、二割引きぃっ……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yellowtail. Yellowtail! Yellowtail!\nT-twenty percent… off?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.50676698691736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 87.57343365358402
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "そこ出遅れてる！　もっとリズム意識して！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re lagging! Focus on the rhythm!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.57343365358402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 91.2903044383435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ふわああぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahhh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.29030443834354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.87273074792911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（ふと周囲を見渡すと、お客さんが大勢集まっている）\n（だが、みな恐る恐る遠巻きに眺めているだけだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I glance around us and see they’ve gathered quite a crowd.)\n(But everyone is just staring timidly from a distance.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.43939741459586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……ダメだこりゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn’t working.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.23939741459586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 103.6727307479292
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 104.33882470137968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "疲れましたわ……\n怜はいつもあのようなことをしてますの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am exhausted.\nRei‚ do you always do work like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0060640812625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
