      "text": "時々ね\nでも慣れればもう少し楽にこなせると思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes‚ yeah.\nBut with a little more experience‚ I think it’ll come easier to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.93939741459585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
